  "title": "[FD] SimpleFreeze",
  "description": "A simple plugin to freeze or unfreeze players",
  "body": "# [FD] SimpleFreeze\n\n**[FD] Simple Freeze** aims to **help you in moderating** your server by allowing you **to freeze or unfreeze any player** on your server.\n\n## Commands\n\nList of commands its here !\n\n### Freeze :\n- Description: Freeze or unfreeze a player\n- Usage: /admin.freeze <player>\n\n## License\n\n<p xmlns:cc=\"http://creativecommons.org/ns#\" xmlns:dct=\"http://purl.org/dc/terms/\"><a property=\"dct:title\" rel=\"cc:attributionURL\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/plugin/fd-simplefreeze/\">FD Simple Freeze</a> by <a rel=\"cc:attributionURL dct:creator\" property=\"cc:attributionName\" href=\"https://mazegroup.org\">FDPlugins, MazeGroup</a> is licensed under <a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/?ref=chooser-v1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"license noopener noreferrer\" style=\"display:inline-block;\">CC BY-NC-SA 4.0<img style=\"height:22px!important;margin-left:3px;vertical-align:text-bottom;\" width=\"22px\" src=\"https://mirrors.creativecommons.org/presskit/icons/cc.svg?ref=chooser-v1\" alt=\"\"><img style=\"height:22px!important;margin-left:3px;vertical-align:text-bottom;\" width=\"22px\" src=\"https://mirrors.creativecommons.org/presskit/icons/by.svg?ref=chooser-v1\" alt=\"\"><img style=\"height:22px!important;margin-left:3px;vertical-align:text-bottom;\" width=\"22px\" src=\"https://mirrors.creativecommons.org/presskit/icons/nc.svg?ref=chooser-v1\" alt=\"\"><img style=\"height:22px!important;margin-left:3px;vertical-align:text-bottom;\" width=\"22px\" src=\"https://mirrors.creativecommons.org/presskit/icons/sa.svg?ref=chooser-v1\" alt=\"\"></a></p>\n</details>\n\nFD SimpleFreeze is a plugin from FreedomSMP (A private SMP)",
